ERROR invalid_set_options
command: ssd set type:alternative label bad --out docs/examples/set-type-alternative-output.ssd --allow-multi docs/examples/minimal.ssd
usage: ssd set <selector> <value-or-field> ... [--stdout|--dry-run|--out <output-file> [--dry-run]] <file>
hint: set output options must appear before the input file, and `--stdout` cannot be combined with `--dry-run` or `--out`; for `type:` set, `--allow-multi` must appear before `--stdout`, `--dry-run`, or `--out`
